e.com/news/music/offset-seemingly-boasts-about-cheating-on-cardi-b-in-new-song-ten-3838053">发行了他的最新单曲“ Ten”，</a>在那里他似乎向孩子的母亲扔下阴影，说唱：“<em>我不需要你，我得到了钱/我不想念你，我有钱/爱你，但不喜欢钱</em>。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="偏移 - 十个（可视化器）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WDJi7RueOHo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他似乎还夸耀在Cardi上作弊：“我不后悔的&#39;bout屎，你的talm&#39;bout&#39;？/你知道一只狗像一只狗一样，像一只罗威纳犬/这么多ho头，当我外出时，我做得最多。”</p><p>自分裂以来，Cardi被发现与NFL明星Stefon Diggs（通过<a href="https://pagesix.com/2025/02/17/celebrity-news/cardi-b-spends-valentines-day-with-texans-wide-receiver-stefon-diggs-after-offset-split/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>第六页</em></a>）一起度过了情人节，并且在与模特Melanie Jayda和<a href="https://www.the-sun.com/entertainment/13053726/offset-spotted-model-anok-yai-cardi-b-split/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anok Yai</a>见面之后，他们在音乐视频中以“十”为“ <a href="https://www.scmp.com/magazines/style/entertainment/article/3293845/meet-melanie-jayda-model-offset-rumoured-be-dating-amid-his-messy-divorce-cardi-b-they-were-spotted?utm_source=chatgpt" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>十</em></a>”。</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/offset-wants-half-of-everything-and-joint-custody-in-divorce-with-cardi-b-3843216">偏移需要一半的一切，而与Cardi B离婚的联合监护权</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
